name: How it works (with cat)
description: An exclusive picture of n picture of a cat that was drawn live in the radio show "Eisenbart & Meisendraht" on Radio Z in order to explain how NFTs work. It was taken on sun, 28th of February 2021. The podcast of the show can be found on www.eisenbartmeisendraht.com or https://eisenbartmeisendraht.podigee.io/ (Episode #0041 - Fake). the picture was also shared on facebook (https://www.facebook.com/eisenbartmeisendraht/photos/a.2145558799031341/2825128544407693)
